Package ePortfolio

Class MutualFund

java.lang.Object
ePortfolio.Investement
ePortfolio.MutualFund
public class MutualFund extends Investement
The MutualFund class represents a mutual fund investment in a financial portfolio. It contains attributes such as the symbol, name, quantity, price, and book value of the mutual fund. The class also includes a constant redemption fee, which is applied when selling the mutual fund. It provides methods for retrieving the mutual fund's attributes. This class does not allow for changes to the redemption fee once it is set, as it is a constant.
